{"tid":2096232,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美制裁加辣 華為5G明年恐難出貨","createTime":"2020-07-06T04:06:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-06T07:26:06.000Z","uid":25558,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"69b6429f7d9f6a029e62b136fe7f9d44925e7cbd","tid":2096232,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T04:06:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200706/2EMBS3LBIJ2DX2THAU7KJWT4ZA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200706%2F2EMBS3LBIJ2DX2THAU7KJWT4ZA%2F&d=HclisOHeH6vmzOJk9j96FouQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=babbcbfc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200706%2F2EMBS3LBIJ2DX2THAU7KJWT4ZA%2F&h=ad40d2d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200706/2EMBS3LBIJ2DX2THAU7KJWT4ZA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n美制裁加辣 華為5G明年恐難出貨<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/HQEWiJAZeRGTwEQeCOIhSd2_5Uo=/640x360/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/E5O423IN37DOC5UDYDD5RBPL7A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FHQEWiJAZeRGTwEQeCOIhSd2_5Uo%3D%2F640x360%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FE5O423IN37DOC5UDYDD5RBPL7A.jpg&h=215ac8aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n英國準備拆除已安裝的華為5G裝置。 <br />\n<br />\n美國今年5月加重對華為的制裁力道，要求採用美國製造設備或依美國軟件與技術設計的半導體商須取得美方許可證，才能向華為供貨，引發各界質疑華為是否能兌現5G合約承諾。有分析師認為，華為明年初開始無法供應5G設備的風險很大，新制裁亦限制台灣台積電等企業向華為出口電腦晶片和其他關鍵零組件。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n專家︰業務非常危險<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：不滿北京推惡法 約翰遜接納國安建議  英封殺華為 鏟5G基建<br />\n<br />\n美國有線電視新聞網（CNN）引述投資銀行傑富瑞（Jefferies）分析師李裕生說：「。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n華為上月借進軍英國市場20年展開宣傳攻勢，<br />\n。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n中央社/BBC"},{"pid":"c96b59ff53fb71f1711a0b228b5859fc1ba95bac","tid":2096232,"uid":155674,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-0